Chelsea football club could have a new owner very soon as Turkish Billionaire businessman, Muhsin Bayrak has declared his interest to purchase the club.

According to the report, he has alleged that his lawyers are in serious discussion with the representative of Roman Abramovich to seal the deal. What then do we know about this Investor?
Personal Life: Muhsin Bayrak migrated to Istanbul, Turkey in the early 1990’s. He obtained his formal education their in turkey.
Businesses And Net worth: He is a business man with investment in Cryptocurrency, Tourism, Construction and Energy. He has been alleged to have a huge work force of about 10,000 persons. His investment is scattered all over the world like Turkey, Spain, United States of America and may be perhaps, his interest in Chelsea football club could bring him into England. He is alleged to be worth over 11 Billion Dollars. Not much is known about his family but he is a married man from an Islamic background.


